{"tid":2065524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫學權威陳肇始局長話遊行會傳播肺炎 去海洋公園 迫地鐵 深圳關口就唔會","createTime":"2020-06-15T15:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T02:57:47.000Z","uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93a5c4882be2bec0ca226b33b57dc7df585bde97","tid":2065524,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:17:17.000Z","msg":"陳肇始昨於網誌稱，港府所有防疫措施均以公共衛生和保護市民健康為原則，「絕無任何政治考慮」，早前有評論指限制群組聚集「政治打壓、針對政治集會」是毫無事實根據。若疫情穩定，不排除在許可情况下逐步放寬群組聚集限制，例如調節群組聚集人數的上限，或增加獲豁免的群組聚集，但無提及撤銷限聚令。<br />\n陳又說，在「粵港澳聯防聯控」基礎上，現似乎「較有條件」有限度放寬從廣東或澳門來港人流，首階段會優先考慮便利必要來往的人。"},{"pid":"7175540a0ab5e16f18e0f1d1edc089fb2380e0ad","tid":2065524,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"大陸話港獨病毒恐怖過武漢肺炎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf21bd12afecedd6b3d7058e0835c9cbcf65e91e","tid":2065524,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"連許樹昌都倒佢米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過睇死柒婆又會再延長限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a368526aff80f6a0f22a6eaca39a32e3a9cacf4","tid":2065524,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf21bd12afecedd6b3d7058e0835c9cbcf65e91e","tid":2065524,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"連許樹昌都倒佢米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過睇死柒婆又會再延長限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"準備到七月中"},{"pid":"8301ee6b473d40c0c2c654f320bcca2c5415d7c9","tid":2065524,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:26:32.000Z","msg":"陳肇始：口交會射精，肛交、無套性交就唔會"},{"pid":"005c31c29d29f7395aa3f07